  <h4>August 1st &amp; August 2nd</h4>

  <div class='hero-info'>
    <p>The fourth annual gathering of Ruby friends in Burlington,
    Vermont, USA.</p>

    <p>Meet folks, enjoy the city, and grow as a Rubyist!</p>

    <p>The 2015 conference is taking place on August 1st and August 2nd
    at <a href='http://www.mainstreetlanding.com/performing-arts-center/'>Main
    St. Landing Film House</a> in Burlington, Vermont, with a Friday evening social gathering
    on July 31st at <a href='http://hotelvt.com/home'>Hotel VT</a>.</p>

    <a href='https://ti.to/burlington-ruby/2015-burlington-ruby-conference' class='button button-primary buy-a-ticket'>Buy a Ticket</a>

    <p>Early tickets are now on sale at $200 a ticket. The price will
    increase to $250 on May 31st, 2015 at 8:00pm EDT.</p>

    <p>Burlington is pretty busy in the summer, so hotels downtown can
    be tough to find. The conference has two hotel blocks that are
    near the conference venue. Be sure to book by June 30th to get the
    block rate.</p>

